## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and expert opinions, which may not cover all aspects of the rapidly evolving field of health informatics. Additionally, the ethical concerns discussed are subject to change as new technologies and regulations emerge. Further research is needed to explore the long-term implications of online health data sharing and the effectiveness of proposed solutions.